<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3740] Session Window State is Not Checkpointed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3740</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The merging window state in the &lt;tt&gt;WindowOperator&lt;/tt&gt; is not checkpointed. This means that programs containing session windows will fail upon restore after a failure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I propose adding a simulated snapshot/restore cycle to the tests in &lt;tt&gt;WindowOperatorTest&lt;/tt&gt; to catch these problems in the future.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
